 event, and we hope to see many entrants. <br>
<br>
We will have the following events:<br>
One-on-One<br>
Free-for-All<br>
Team Battles (Groups of 6) If there is enough entrants<br>
<br>
The events are broken into the following level brackets:<br>
Levels 1-3<br>
Levels 4-7<br>
Levels 8-9 <br>
Levels 10-11<br>
<br>
Prizes will be awarded to the winners of each event. Random EQ trivia questions will be asked during events, and prizes will be awarded for these as well. Come out and show your support for player-driven events by participating or watching. For more details, visit our Arena Tournament page at <a href="http://silverdaggers.freehosting.net/tourney.html ">silverdaggers.freehosting.net/tourney.html </a>where you can also fill out an entry form. <br>
